solves everything.

141
00:06:22.516 --> 00:06:23.450
Pizza's fine.

142
00:06:23.584 --> 00:06:25.086
Pepperoni. bitches.

143
00:06:25.219 --> 00:06:26.453
- Hey. J.D.
- Yeah.

144
00:06:26.587 --> 00:06:27.822
Tosh is gonna
get you on the apps.

145
00:06:27.955 --> 00:06:29.957
Okay. no. I did say
it was a bad idea.

146
00:06:30.091 --> 00:06:33.127
It is a lot of
just half-naked women
trying to get a free dinner.

147
00:06:33.261 --> 00:06:35.096
Yeah. and Carla said
I get to swipe for you.

148
00:06:35.229 --> 00:06:37.231
The thing is. I think
I may have already met someone.

149
00:06:37.365 --> 00:06:39.000
See. man. I knew you were
gonna mess this up for us.

150
00:06:39.133 --> 00:06:42.336
She's an angel.
She's a beautiful lobby angel.

151
00:06:42.469 --> 00:06:43.704
The harp player?

152
00:06:43.838 --> 00:06:45.339
- Yeah.
- Buddy. she works here.

153
00:06:45.472 --> 00:06:46.908
and Park's gunning for you.

154
00:06:47.041 --> 00:06:49.377
If you dip your toe
or any other part of yourself

155
00:06:49.510 --> 00:06:50.845
in the dating pool
at this hospital.

156
00:06:50.978 --> 00:06:53.014
he's gonna use it
to bring you down.

157
00:06:53.147 --> 00:06:55.816
Park sleeps with everyone.
He does laps
in the hospital dating pool.

158
00:06:55.950 --> 00:06:57.985
and he swims both ways.
if you know what I mean.

159
00:06:58.119 --> 00:07:00.621
Right. But he only sleeps
with attendings or above.

160
00:07:00.755 --> 00:07:04.926
So unless your harp player
is chief of harp playing.
don't go there. bro.

161
00:07:05.059 --> 00:07:06.727
Yeah. you're right.
Actually. that's good advice.

162
00:07:06.861 --> 00:07:08.129
Thank you. Good looking out.

163
00:07:08.262 --> 00:07:10.463
Okay. well.
if we are back on the apps.

164
00:07:10.598 --> 00:07:13.167
I think with a few filters.
maybe a ring light.
maybe a puppy to pose with.

165
00:07:13.301 --> 00:07:15.770
I think a few seniors would
probably swipe right on you.

166
00:07:15.903 --> 00:07:18.205
Seniors? How old
do you think I am?

167
00:07:18.339 --> 00:07:19.874
-Si...
-"Si..."?

168
00:07:20.007 --> 00:07:22.243
-I think I should probably go.
-Yeah. that's a good idea.

169
00:07:22.376 --> 00:07:23.577
She said "si."

170
00:07:23.711 --> 00:07:25.179
Yeah. "si" was crazy.

171
00:07:26.747 --> 00:07:28.182
Oh. my God. it's happening.

172
00:07:28.316 --> 00:07:30.918
The liver donor's off
life support.

173
00:07:31.052 --> 00:07:34.021
I can't. in good conscience.
