-Now I just saw
your ex-husband.

180
00:07:48.703 --> 00:07:50.171
And. baby...

181
00:07:50.304 --> 00:07:51.872
-You know that harp player
in the lobby?
-Mm-hmm.

182
00:07:52.006 --> 00:07:54.408
He's trying to be
the next thing that she plucks.

183
00:07:54.542 --> 00:07:56.043
When are you
getting back out there?

184
00:07:56.177 --> 00:07:58.112
-Oh--
-It's too late for her.
She'd rather die alone.

185
00:07:58.245 --> 00:08:00.581
Paraphrasing.
but that's what she said.
word for word.

186
00:08:00.715 --> 00:08:04.218
I didn't say that!
I just said that dating
post-divorce sounds terrible.

187
00:08:04.352 --> 00:08:06.821
and I would rather die alone!
Okay. fine. I'm saying it now.

188
00:08:06.954 --> 00:08:10.224
Free yourself. Get out there
and throw that ass in a circle.

189
00:08:10.358 --> 00:08:13.160
- Yeah. divorce like a man.
Be messy.
- Mm-hmm.

190
00:08:13.294 --> 00:08:15.495
