to talk about.
-It's never gonna happen.

191
00:08:15.629 --> 00:08:16.797
I'm fine.

192
00:08:16.931 --> 00:08:18.265
Oh. you could
spread that around.

193
00:08:18.833 --> 00:08:22.269
Now. why would I do that?
Don't nobody care
when somebody is fine.

194
00:08:22.970 --> 00:08:26.140
Do two extra-large pizzas say.
"We're sorry."
or. "You guys eat a lot."

195
00:08:26.273 --> 00:08:28.242
and then we're just
insulting them all over again?

196
00:08:28.376 --> 00:08:30.378
You know.
I could've done this alone.

197
00:08:30.511 --> 00:08:32.546
I'd have
the same amount of pizza.
but with twice as much quiet.

198
00:08:32.680 --> 00:08:34.615
Sorry.

199
00:08:34.749 --> 00:08:36.484
I tend to talk a lot
when the person I'm with
is brooding and mysterious.

200
00:08:36.617 --> 00:08:38.085
Were your parents
killed by the Joker?

201
00:08:38.219 --> 00:08:39.954
Because you're really
giving off Bruce Wayne vibes.

202
00:08:40.087 --> 00:08:41.956
There's a guy following us.
all right?

203
00:08:42.089 --> 00:08:44.158
He's gonna rob us.
but he's not gonna hurt us.
Stay calm.

204
00:08:45.459 --> 00:08:46.894
Stop! That's my purse!

205
00:08:47.461 --> 00:08:51.399
Ooh. that's a concussion.
I'm gonna go get my bag
while he's out.

206
00:08:52.033 --> 00:08:55.302
So. Pauline. what's
the first thing you'll do
when you get out of here?

207
00:08:55.436 --> 00:08:57.506
I'll tell you when
they put the liver in me. kid.

208
00:08:57.638 --> 00:09:00.775
If it were me.
I'd get on a plane to England
and take my mum to tea.

209
00:09:00.908 --> 00:09:02.610
Boring.

210
00:09:02.743 --> 00:09:03.944
Mine's much better.

211
00:09:04.078 --> 00:09:05.713
Oh. see? She does have a plan.

212
00:09:05.846 --> 00:09:07.516
Okay. I don't know
about the liver.

213
00:09:07.648 --> 00:09:10.384
but my body is rejecting
this positivity.

214
00:09:14.889 --> 00:09:17.291
Pauline. could you excuse us
