and can't be implanted.

217
00:09:25.966 --> 00:09:29.570
I can't go in there
for a third time and tell her
it's not happening.

218
00:09:30.539 --> 00:09:31.806
I gotta fix this.

219
00:09:33.641 --> 00:09:35.743
This kid needs to be admitted.
Possible concussion.

220
00:09:35.876 --> 00:09:39.380
Okay. what I'm seeing
is you came back with more work
for us and no pizza.

221
00:09:39.514 --> 00:09:41.949
He mugged us.
The pizzas were also victims.

222
00:09:42.083 --> 00:09:43.117
Oh. my God. are you okay?

223
00:09:43.250 --> 00:09:45.219
-We're gonna--
-Excuse you.

224
